title: Snaps - Auburn fires Bryan Harsin, Deion Sanders or Lane Kiffin possible replacement?
itunes:title: Snaps - Auburn fires Bryan Harsin, Deion Sanders or Lane Kiffin possible replacement?
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert react to Auburn firing head coach Bryan Harsin after his 9-12 record with the Tigers. Could former Carolina Panthers head coach Matt Rhule, Jackson State head coach Deion Sanders, or Ole Miss head coach Lane Kiffin be in line to take over Auburn's football program? #Volume #ColinCowherd #Herd
